spec_data.Name: texlive-ucharcat
spec_data.Description:
The package implements the \Ucharcat command for LuaLaTeX.
\Ucharcat is a new primitive in XeTeX, an extension of the
existing \Uchar command, that allows the specification of the
catcode as well as character code of the character token being
constructed.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:48:26 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Implementation of the (new in 2015) XeTeX \Ucharcat command in lua, for LuaTeX
